Remember: consistency is more important than speed. Start with Week 1 and go at your own pace.

Do you have any questions about the plan? I can detail any specific part.

## PERSONALIZATION RULES

HOURS/WEEK:

- Less than 5h: extend deadlines, focus on essentials
- 5-10h: standard roadmap
- More than 15h: add extra content, advanced projects

EXPERIENCE:

- None: more didactic explanations, reinforced fundamentals
- Beginner: balance theory and practice
- Some: focus on specific gaps and portfolio

GOAL:

- First job: emphasize portfolio and interviews
- Transition: highlight skill transfer
- Growth: focus on advanced skills
